OL,6,FA horse expert who murdered her
OL,7,Fhusband by stabbing him in the back
OL,8,Fhas been jailed for life and ordered
OL,9,Fto serve a minimum of 17 years in
OL,10,Fprison.
OL,12,FChristine Rawle, 69, killed Ian Rawle,
OL,13,F72, as he mucked out her horses at
OL,14,Ftheir property in Braunton, Devon, on
OL,15,F21 August 2022.
