OL,6,FExeter Crown Court previously heard Mr
OL,7,FRawle then followed his wife of 27
OL,8,Fyears for 100 yards telling her to
OL,9,Fremove the knife, before collapsing
OL,10,Fand dying from the wound.
OL,12,FThe judge told Rawle: "You said to the
OL,13,Fpolice that you were frightened of
OL,14,Fyour husband. But he was a 72-year-old
OL,15,Fman with a knife in his back. He
OL,16,Fwanted you to help him. But it seems
OL,17,Fto me you refused to do so."
